// EDIT PROFILE //
"http://localhost:8000/edit-profile"

I'll send 2 parameters:
    1. username:
        - if it's  an empty string -> do nothing
        - If it's not an empty string -> check if username already exists:
            - if it exists -> send an error
            - if it does not -> change username on DDBB and reply front
    2. Avatar:
        - if it's  an empty file -> do nothing
        - If it's not an empty file ->
            - generate name
            - save file to avatars
            - change rote on BBDD
            - send front new route

// FRIENDS //
"http://localhost:8000/friends"

GET -> send front all friends

POST -> I'll send 1 parameter: username
    - if user doesn't exist -> send front an error
    - if user exist -> add to friends and send reply to front

// PUBLIC PROFILE //
"http://localhost:8000/public-profile"

I'll send 1 parameter: username
    - if user doesn't exist -> send front an error
    - if user exist -> send public profile to front

// CHATS //

"http://localhost:8000/chats"

GET-> send all the chat for the user

"http://localhost:8000/chats/user"

GET -> I'll send a username as parameter
    - if user doesn't exist -> send front an error
    - if user exist -> send all messages between user(parameter) and user(token)

// CHATROOMS //

"http://localhost:8000/chatrooms"

GET-> send all the chatrooms for the user



